                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Sefer ha-goralot</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">ספר הגורלות</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>A book of lots, based on the correspondence between the twelve signs of Zodiac and sixty biblical prophets and forefathers. </p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>A long prayer begins on folio 1v, then follows a table of the signs of Zodiac (folio 2r), with questions and references to partsufim in parallel columns. The table of partsufim begins on folio 3r, and the table of answers on folio 4r. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
               
               
               
               </msContents>
               
               
               
